{% submission %}

{% submission-part type="problem" %}

Keeping track of high frequency words and tracking when they are ready to move to the next group. Also, how to easily test only the words that they have not mastered yet and by mixing up the order every time.

{% /submission-part %}

{% submission-part type="proposed-solution" %}

It would be fantastic if we had an app that could be broken down by students and in each student track their progress by allowing randomizing of the group they’re in and once they’ve mastered that it only shows up in an occasional review before moving onto the next group of words. Teachers could make their own sets of words or have a feature where they can auto populate either the DOLCH or FRYE words based on whatever curriculum they use

{% /submission-part %}

{% /submission %}